Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:02:00.87,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}たとえピースが揃っても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:02:00.87,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}就算Piece全部集齊
